HEADWORD: Peppery
<hw>Pep"per*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or
pertaining to pepper; having the qualities of pepper; hot;
pungent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: Hot-tempered; passionate; choleric.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>peppy</ent>⟦br⟧
